{"tid":1634310,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"［文宣戰］裝修獅鳥只係第一步，挑撥離間先係重點！","createTime":"2019-10-07T07:22:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T15:32:00.000Z","uid":21678,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"eecbe753eeb8447144ff4ee822b507d280184646","tid":1634310,"uid":21678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:22:37.000Z","msg":"港共其實明知反蒙面法係雙面刃<br />\n如果唔係<br />\n十月一日之前早就用咗<br />\n唔駛畀人響國慶落中共面<br />\n<br />\n咁呢把「雙面刃」<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">傷及自己嘅地方響邊？</span></strong><br />\n就係響惡法下，示威者唔可以集結<br />\n怒氣化整為零<br />\n然後區區開花突擊親政府商舖<br />\n亦即係「黑裝修同紅裝飾」<br />\n<br />\n如果要煲大政府自損嘅程度<br />\n就應該學習對方「人民鬥人民」嘅方針<br />\n即係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>挑釁政界同商界之間嘅矛盾</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n所以<br />\n示威者嘅文宣<br />\n以示威者角度嘅聲明就算嘈到拆天<br />\n對方都係嗤之以鼻、唔會理你；<br />\n相反<br />\n如果發聲嘅係本身支持政府嘅人呢？<br />\n政府可唔可以再唔出聲？<br />\n<br />\n具體行動<br />\n就係響被裝修嘅地點、連儂牆、網上流傳WhatsApp Cap圖、藍絲Fan Page... etc<br />\n以小商戶/中立巿民/商界身份<br />\n宣揚一句簡單口號：<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「林鄭月娥<br />\n今次畀你累死！」</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"4570d2b674238d62b7c3898735e681d0ee30c078","tid":1634310,"uid":9448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:22:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1e19e053ca1b0f01c5244c74fe927aced6264031","tid":1634310,"uid":43469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:23:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43555ebe42bd57fee06534fb892bc9fbb9ca3831","tid":1634310,"uid":21678,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:24:14.000Z","msg":"呢句嘢有幾個重點：<br />\n<br />\n1.講呢句說話嘢人背後嘅人設<br />\n唔係黃絲、唔係暴徒<br />\n而係藍絲同一般商戶<br />\n咁先可以激起敵方內部同理心<br />\n繼而誘發分岐<br />\n<br />\n2.指控必定要有名有姓<br />\n集中焦點<br />\n因為指摘中共/習近平<br />\n會令好多藍絲渾身不自在<br />\n所以暫時幫佢哋聚焦落林鄭一個人身上<br />\n係最好嘅目標<br />\n<br />\n3.既然文宣係用嚟挑釁藍絲<br />\n就要放響佢哋同溫層裡面<br />\n包括被裝修店舖門外<br />\n總之要吹到連藍絲阿婆都識講：<br />\n「最衰都係林鄭啦」云云"},{"pid":"4c1292012d2f41ae03caa830f94bf5d6751624f7","tid":1634310,"uid":21678,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:27:11.000Z","msg":"港共內部<br />\n一定有支持緊急法嘅人<br />\n亦一樣有反對用呢條大絕嘅聲音<br />\n所以需要製造一啲畀林鄭敵人可以使用嘅武器"},{"pid":"2529130ac52fe9e14a1a9d240f72a886eee748c5","tid":1634310,"uid":21678,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:31:04.000Z","msg":"試想吓<br />\n如果有間裝修店面貼住<br />\n「林鄭，我哋畀你搞成咁」<br />\n<br />\n對於深藍嘅人有咩睇法？<br />\n肯定覺得佢無能<br />\n為咗自己向北京交功課<br />\n而犧牲咗呢班支持者"},{"pid":"eb4f540018a7ef68979f51a0eb98348d20ec0a1f","tid":1634310,"uid":289350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:36:12.000Z","msg":"P 牌推"},{"pid":"1fed03dd83a6cf790bf7b9580709b31918e95e4c","tid":1634310,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:37:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a700f0a4ce4358a1cac318042ac13968c7d71e52","tid":1634310,"uid":21678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:48:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a9487dbc6bc035b790ce74e4d880960079566dcf","tid":1634310,"uid":21678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:53:33.000Z","msg":"同埋政府而家賭緊一舖<br />\n搏緊大眾巿民會同裝修小隊割蓆<br />\n<br />\n如果藍色紅色商戶率先同林鄭割蓆<br />\n就將會係佢呢一隊人嘅末日"},{"pid":"6afd71f69e04ebc3b6691f89144cfdeb4928f80f","tid":1634310,"uid":21678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:57:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4c5f9e5f72db3e29427847232771eebe557fa53f","tid":1634310,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:59:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JG49P0v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJG49P0v.jpg&h=bfdca82e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行動Post : <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1634329\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1634329</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">目標一、哂馬</span></strong></span><br />\n由於警狗唔再批不反，即使批左亦會製造衝突。<br />\n為左令和理非可以舒舒服服地出返黎，展示人數同民意，<br />\n所以就利用黃店門外既人龍，製造畫面同話題吸引媒體注意。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">目標二、支持黃色經濟</span></span></strong><br />\n依幾個月生意難免受影響，加上可能被藍絲杯葛，<br />\n良心黃店係好需要大家支持。<br />\n最實際既支持當然就係拎銀包出黎，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>入錢入錢入錢！</strong></span><br />\n另外參考連登既食評，由於良心經營既關係，黃店食物質素一般都偏高，<br />\n絕對係win win雙贏！<br />\n<br />\n------------國際文宣------------<br />\n請將買返黎既貨物/食物/單據同排隊盛況<br />\n一齊用<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">#Buy4HK</span></span></strong><br />\n放上IG, Twitter, reddit"},{"pid":"ab5f1474cdb248129dad0c7e437aa528b4b73ad8","tid":1634310,"uid":106937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:59:16.000Z","msg":"Please follow: <br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/lee_cobaj\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flee_cobaj&d=fuRTyfFj%2BaUlIJflnhZSn6C2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=0343ea8f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/lee_cobaj</a> <br />\n<a href=\"http://guardiansofhk.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fguardiansofhk.com%2F&d=fuRTyfFj%2BaUlIJflnhZSn6C2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=d581e964\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://guardiansofhk.com/</a>"},{"pid":"2d8e1b83c2166c823566a6792ca5861a86410a0e","tid":1634310,"uid":106937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:01:41.000Z","msg":"Please follow: <br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/lee_cobaj\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flee_cobaj&d=fuRTyfFj%2BaUlIJflnhZSn6C2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=0343ea8f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/lee_cobaj</a> <br />\n<a href=\"http://guardiansofhk.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fguardiansofhk.com%2F&d=fuRTyf